A Dream of Summer
Company: Milk Cat
Release date: Aug 01, 2005
Rating: All Ages
Language: English Subtitled
Genre: Visual Novel

Summary: Toshiki, the realist. Mizuna, the girl he met on the roof. And BROY, the school band whose members surround them. It's the summer of their third year, and Toshiki must face not only the school festival, but also a promise that he may never be able to fulfill.


Translator: DejaVu 


